2025-09-18PS, EPCREmergency Management ActProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 282, YukonProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 282 in order to (1) declare the natural disaster to be of concern to the federal government; and (2) authorize the provision of financial assistance to Yukon with respect to the interface fires that occurred from June 20 to August 21, 2024.N/A
subject: Provincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 282, Yukon
precis: Provincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 282 in order to (1) declare the natural disaster to be of concern to the federal government; and (2) authorize the provision of financial assistance to Yukon with respect to the interface fires that occurred from June 20 to August 21, 2024.
